text: Diadelia fuscostictica is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Baguena Corella and Breuning in 1958.BioLib.cz - Diadelia fuscostictica. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Diadelia Category:Beetles described in 1958
